            <div class="right-column" data-aos="fade-left">
                                    <h2>Why both?</h2>
<p>Large consulting companies have been offering GRC software and risk advisory services since their inception. Why? Because there is a need.  Organisations require advice, strategic planning and the tools to automate risk &amp; compliance processes from a single provider.</p>
                            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>




