            <div class="right-column" data-aos="fade-left">
                                    <h2>Digital transformation</h2>
<p>The nature of consulting engagements is changing though.  Businesses need deep, ongoing relationships, which focus on access to insight and outcomes rather than isolated  projects. Cloud platforms are central to this idea, transforming the way software and professional services are consumed.</p>
                            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>




